long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Save your active enrollments to your Google Calendar or download them as a .ics Universal Calendar File.

Features
- Automatically syncs active enrollments to your Google Calendar
- Shows scheduling conflicts between events online and your Google Calendar
- Download .ics calendar file with current enrollments
